thread.title: Protests hit Nairobi as crackdown on opposition deepens

title: Protests hit Nairobi as crackdown on opposition deepens
text:
Protests hit Nairobi as crackdown on opposition deepens 5:31pm GMT - 01:21 
An opposition lawyer was arrested and three private television stations remain banned as new protests hit Nairobi challenging President Uhuru Kenyatta's authority. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
